e4thcom: 0.8.4 \ test.efc : plug-in for target protocol evaluation     MM-150211

cr <brown .( * Loading plug-in test.efc for target protocol evaluation.) normal>

cr .(    * The e4thcom directory must be the current working directory !)
cr .(    * Enter  #i test [Enter]  or  #i TEST [Enter]  to test the targets response.)
cr

e4thcom-0.8.4 definitions decimal

:noname ( oid -- flag )
   \ Wait while the target evakuates a line of uploaded code. Return a true
   \ flag on error, a false flag otherwise.
   >self  self rx-buf erase  1000 self timeout !  white bright letters
   ." |>"
   begin
     self rx?timeout ( c f ) if drop cr false exit then
     ( c ) dup self rx-buf append
     ( c ) dup bl <
     if \ c = control char
       ( c ) [char] ^ emit base @ swap hex s>d <# # #s #> type base !
     else
       self ?emit
     then
   again ;

terminal plug-in !

